  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in the world of intrigue and art scandals with Arts&Hearts Academy. You'll shiver but beg for more!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2659250/extras/0634f8da1960424411f3dfc353881092.avif?t=1734185570\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2659250/extras_big/0634f8da1960424411f3dfc353881092.avif?t=1734185570 width=800 height=161 /></span>A girl from a provincial architecture college dreams of winning a prestigious competition. But everything seems to be against her: hostile competitors, disagreements inside her team, and secrets hidden within the walls of the Architecture Academy. She must uncover the long-forgotten disappearance of a student or risk repeating her fate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2659250/extras/fd4bc7e46a54891083472d16b30bb628.avif?t=1734185570\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2659250/extras_big/fd4bc7e46a54891083472d16b30bb628.avif?t=1734185570 width=800 height=161 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2659250/extras/86b9f86385d0f4f93fd8a5e445740e9a.avif?t=1734185570\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2659250/extras_big/86b9f86385d0f4f93fd8a5e445740e9a.avif?t=1734185570 width=800 height=161 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ryan</strong> - an architectural genius and the friendliest guy in college. Everyone adores him.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2659250/extras/483e68818e00d5414c685f6ffb2ba94f.avif?t=1734185570\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2659250/extras_big/483e68818e00d5414c685f6ffb2ba94f.avif?t=1734185570 width=800 height=161 /></span><strong>Lucien</strong> - the heir to an architectural conglomerate, a cold and proud team captain.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2659250/extras/7db38008fa5a8f74c90149ce27a22e8b.avif?t=1734185570\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2659250/extras_big/7db38008fa5a8f74c90149ce27a22e8b.avif?t=1734185570 width=800 height=161 /></span><strong>Theo</strong> - the rival team’s captain, charming and cunning.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2659250/extras/a538459ac6d59edd5070eee6dda5c444.avif?t=1734185570\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2659250/extras_big/a538459ac6d59edd5070eee6dda5c444.avif?t=1734185570 width=800 height=161 /></span>• 3 unique love interests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• A nonlinear storyline with over 12 different endings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• The possibility to play as a good or morally grey character.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• A deep dive into the world of architecture and art.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Dark Academia aesthetics and an unexpected detective twist.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in the world of intrigue and art scandals with Arts&Hearts Academy. You'll shiver but beg for more!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2659250/extras/0634f8da1960424411f3dfc353881092.avif?t=1734185570\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2659250/extras_big/0634f8da1960424411f3dfc353881092.avif?t=1734185570 width=800 height=161 /></span>A girl from a provincial architecture college dreams of winning a prestigious competition. But everything seems to be against her: hostile competitors, disagreements inside her team, and secrets hidden within the walls of the Architecture Academy. She must uncover the long-forgotten disappearance of a student or risk repeating her fate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2659250/extras/fd4bc7e46a54891083472d16b30bb628.avif?t=1734185570\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2659250/extras_big/fd4bc7e46a54891083472d16b30bb628.avif?t=1734185570 width=800 height=161 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2659250/extras/86b9f86385d0f4f93fd8a5e445740e9a.avif?t=1734185570\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2659250/extras_big/86b9f86385d0f4f93fd8a5e445740e9a.avif?t=1734185570 width=800 height=161 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ryan</strong> - an architectural genius and the friendliest guy in college. Everyone adores him.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2659250/extras/483e68818e00d5414c685f6ffb2ba94f.avif?t=1734185570